# Updater signing private key. The PUBLIC key lives in tauri.conf.json and is
# safe to commit; the PRIVATE key must never be committed. Supply it at build
# time via TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY (see docs/desktop-signing.md).
/.tauri-updater-key
/.tauri-updater-key.pub
